Usage

  acme [options] [<target>]

Arguments

  [<target>]  Target to operate on

Filters

  -O, --owner <owner>    Owner/organization

      --archived         Include archived
  -l, --language <lang>  Filter by language

  -i <regex>             Filter by regex
  --include <name>       Include by exact name

Options

  -b, --branch <name>    Branch to use
  -Q, --quick            Quick mode
      --method <type>    Method [ssh, https]

  -n, --dry              Dry run
  -q, --quiet            Suppress output
  -v, --verbose          Verbose output

Examples

  # Basic usage
  $ acme target

  # With filters
  $ acme --language=Go all
